														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-720259">
									

<p>I would think it is a bit too useful to be able to take items out of stories. What would stop someone from writing about a device that could destroy/incapacitate SCP-682 in the world of the story? Not saying it will work outside the story, but still…</p>
<p>Maybe have items taken out of the story begin to break down slowly, like reduce to dust and vanish in a few hours? That would lower the overly useful factor.</p>

							</div>

								
					
