														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-720366">
									

<p>Good point - I guess my logic was I wanted to feel like monsters and whatnot from books and movies could be brought out of SCP-826, as an attempt to up the scare factor. But then that would probably fall into "it makes more SCPs" territory.</p>
<p>What about going with the "background character" idea? That anyone who uses items taken out of the story start developing the memories and traits of a background character within the story, before finally disappearing into the story itself within a few hours?</p>

							</div>

								
					
